origin.moonlight.moobloom.name: Moobloom
power.moonlight.moobloom.flower_trail.de: You leave a trail of dandelions as you walk.
power.moonlight.moobloom.milk_bucket.des: Sneaking and right-clicking while holding a bucket will fill it with milk.
power.moonlight.moobloom.no_netherite.de: Netherite armor is too heavy for you to wear.
power.moonlight.moobloom.regen.name: The Cutest of Cows
power.moonlight.moobloom.regen.descripti: Nearby players are charmed by you and regenerate health more quickly.
power.moonlight.moobloom.size.name: Cow-sized
power.moonlight.moobloom.size.descriptio: You're smaller than a normal player, only being 1.5 blocks tall.
power.moonlight.moobloom.vegetarian.name: Vegetarian
power.moonlight.moobloom.vegetarian.desc: You can only eat wheat and plant-based foods.
Your body mass makes it hard to walk while in water.
